===Etymology===
Old English [[Lindcoln]], from Latin [[Lindum Colonia]], from Brythonic [[Lindo]], [[Lindon]], probably from ''*linn'' ‘pool’, in reference to the [[w:Brayford Pool|Brayford]].

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/'lɪŋkən/}}

===Proper noun===
{{en-noun|Lincoln|Lincolns}}

