# A city in [[Nebraska]], [[USA]].
# A city in [[Illinois]], [[USA]].
# A town in [[Maine]], [[USA]].
# A town in [[California]], [[USA]].
# A town in [[Argentina]].
# A brand of American [[automobile]].
# An English breed of [[sheep]].
# An English [[surname]].

